+      string-compares these at runtime and REFUSES on any drift, Rule 1.8);
+  (c) the falsifiable predictions with units declared;
+  (d) the `expectations` (ground-truth values graded against);
+  (e) `status_move_rules` encoding R2 (the channels are frame-relative in the
+      supplied DBP frame; only the sum K_G = sigma_2 is intrinsic; the
+      single-edge law is a SYMBOLIC IDENTITY over Q in (t,g,H)) and the K4
+      armed kill;
+  (f) `depends_on` = sha256 of the manifest + EVERY bench module the battery
+      executes;
+  (g) the referee description, frozen:true, version.
+
+This builder is run ONCE to freeze the prereg. It does NOT grade and is NOT the
+battery; it only assembles the frozen object deterministically (sorted keys).
+
+PATHS are derived RELOCATABLY from this file's location: STAGE is this file's
+directory; RESULTS is its parent; the frozen authority objects (manifest /
+SCHEMA / FIXTURES / ledger / freeze_pins) are read from the worktree copy under
