+# depends_on: manifest + EVERY bench module the Stage-C battery executes.
+# Stage C executes the probe (Path A organ), referee_total (Path B),
+# referee_channel (Path B'), oracle (Path C), fixtures (operand generator /
+# Stage-0 control / keystone F8 base jet), schema (record type + role gate +
+# the verbatim closure identities/type gates).
+# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
