+    "gauge_law_verbatim": (
+        "SINGLE-EDGE GAUGE (Stage C, declared DBP frame). The gauge is the "
+        "border shear acting on the jet (g, H): g is UNCHANGED; "
+        "H -> H + t*(g e_i^T + e_i g^T), i.e. H[a][c] += t*(g[a]*[c==i] + "
